NOTE ON THE UNDERLYING WORK

The Arabic Tafsir al-Qur'an al-'Azim (Tafsir Ibn Kathir) by Isma'il ibn Kathir
(d. 774 AH / 1373 CE) is in the PUBLIC DOMAIN. The English text in this
repository is an independent translation of that public-domain Arabic and is not
derived from any copyrighted translation. See PROVENANCE.md.
